graph TB
    subgraph "ODH Notebook Controller"
        Controller[OpenshiftNotebookReconciler<br/>Watches Notebook CRs]
        Webhook[NotebookWebhook<br/>Mutating Admission]
        Manager[Manager Deployment<br/>Port: 8080 metrics, 8081 health, 8443 webhook]

        Controller -->|runs in| Manager
        Webhook -->|runs in| Manager
    end

    subgraph "Kubernetes Resources Created"
        Route[OpenShift Route<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS Edge/Reencrypt]
        Service[Service<br/>ClusterIP]
        ServiceAccount[ServiceAccount<br/>OAuth integration]
        Secret[Secrets<br/>OAuth config, TLS certs]
        NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicy<br/>Ingress rules]
    end

    subgraph "User Notebook Pod (OAuth Enabled)"
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy Sidecar<br/>Port: 8443/TCP<br/>Image: ose-oauth-proxy]
        NotebookContainer[Notebook Container<br/>Port: 8888/TCP<br/>JupyterLab/RStudio]

        OAuthProxy -->|proxies to| NotebookContainer
    end

    User[User/Data Scientist] -->|creates| NotebookCR[Notebook CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]

    NotebookCR -->|triggers| Webhook
    Webhook -->|injects OAuth sidecar| NotebookCR

    NotebookCR -->|watched by| Controller
    NotebookCR -->|processed by| KubeflowController[Kubeflow Notebook Controller<br/>Creates StatefulSet]

    Controller -->|creates/updates| Route
    Controller -->|creates/updates| Service
    Controller -->|creates/updates| ServiceAccount
    Controller -->|creates/updates| Secret
    Controller -->|creates/updates| NetworkPolicy

    Route -->|routes to| Service
    Service -->|targets| OAuthProxy

    OAuthProxy -->|authenticates via| OpenShiftOAuth[OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    OAuthProxy -->|authorizes via| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>SubjectAccessReview]

    Controller -->|CRUD operations| K8sAPI
    Controller -->|depends on| ServiceCA[Service CA Operator<br/>Auto-provisions TLS]

    ServiceAccount -->|OAuth redirect| Route

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Manager fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style NotebookCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OAuthProxy fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style NotebookContainer fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OpenShiftOAuth fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServiceCA fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style KubeflowController fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
